node.text:
‘Mission Impossible’
‼️OFFICIALLY the craziest project I’ve had the pleasure of putting together. **Every single stone is GIA Certified VVS1, D colorless** 💪🏽🤯 
~ Set in @thecrowncollection signature Tri-Tone 👑 
_
When a good friend inquired about making this custom chain, I knew teaming up with @jacobmiiori to create this was the best route for knocking it out of the park!
_
Enjoy 📈

node.text:
Truly a museum quality work of art. 
It doesn’t get much better than this 8.53ct Colombian Emerald surrounded by 10+ carats of certified Internally Flawless to VS Diamonds, set in 18k Gold.
Designed and created by @hm.jewelry
_
If you’re interested in commissioning a piece of this caliber, Hayden would love to do something special for you.
Please DM @thecrowncollection to inquire 👑
